basicInfo.name: Barbeque Nation
basicInfo.cuisine_string: North Indian, BBQ, Biryani, Kebab, Continental, Chinese, Beverages, Desserts

establishment.address: 101, 1st Floor, Golden Square, Parle Point, Airport Road, Near Sagam Shopping Complex, Athwa, Surat

items.name: Barbeque In A Box (Veg) Premium
items.description: [Six Starters] - Tandoori Paneer Tikka (4 Pcs) + Churrasco Pineapple (6 Pcs) + Veg Kebabs (6 Pcs) + Veg Rolls (6 Pcs) + Cheese Triangle (6 Pcs) + Assorted Grilled Corn & Veg (2 Nos) [Main Course] - Paneer Butter Masala + Mix Veg + Dal Makhani + Veg Dum Biryani + Whole Wheat Paratha (3 Nos) [Three Desserts] Angoori Jamun (8 Pcs) + Moong Dal Halwa + Brownie. Accompanied with Mint Chutney, Salan, Dips & Salad. Barbeque Nation buffet served at home.

items.name: Boneless Chicken Biryani

items.name: Chicken Biryani
items.description: Chicken marinated in house blend of Indian spices and layered between aromatic rice. Served with Raita.

items.name: Chicken Tikka Biryani
items.description: Boneless Chicken chunks marinated in  authentic tikka masala and grilled on skewers and layered between aromatic rice. Served with Raita &  Salan. Kcal - 814

items.name: Paneer Tikka Biryani
items.description: Cottage Cheese marinated in Indian spices and hung curd cooked in clay oven -Tandoor layered with aromatic rice. Served with Salan & Raita. Kcal - 803

items.name: Mutton Biryani
items.description: Succulent pieces of mutton slow cooked on bed of aromatic rice with in-house blend of spices and seasonings and served with raita. Kcal - 1227

items.name: Prawns Biryani

items.name: Veg Biryani

items.name: Butter Chicken
items.description: One of the most popular Punjabi style chicken dishes in the world , cooked in tomato puree, cream, butter and a host of masalas. Kcal - 663

items.description: Rich creamy dish of cottage cheese chunks cooked  in a tomato  and cashew paste. mild sweet taste ,recommended with naan or flavoured rice. Kcal - 694

items.name: Dal Makhani
items.description: India's most loved and sought after Dal. lentils slowly simmered in a very aromatic buttery, creamy tomato sauce.  Kcal - 429
